        <dc:creator><![CDATA[cadbloke]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>So I still have a year or 2 to go before I launch <a href="http://cadfindreplace.com.au/" rel="nofollow noopener">http://cadfindreplace.com.au/</a>  …the earliest version I can find is at <a href="http://cadbloke.com/2011/08/18/cadtools-the-early-years/" rel="nofollow noopener">http://cadbloke.com/2011/08/18/cadtools-the-early-years/</a> - it’s the top one. Cool, I can slack off a bit.</p>
