        <title>Overnight success in just 3652 days</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Christopher]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p>I dunno, Dave.  Rob had a long, twisty road to get to Drip.  Josh learned from his early successes with the Apple blog and the toy biz.  Ruben went the lon way 'round as well, if I recall.</p>
<p>But OK, by the time they went into those businesses with all that hard-won knowledge, I’ll grant you that the software DID come around in record time!  <img src="https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=5" title=":stuck_out_tongue:" class="emoji" alt=":stuck_out_tongue:"></p>
